item.title: Tennis Holidays
item.description: Tennis Holidays About My Dad and I have run St. Lucia Tennis holidays for Oshawa Tennis Club players, their friends and other Durham region players for the last 4 years. The idea behind the tennis holiday was to give a unique tour of St. Lucia with my dad and myself who grew up on the island. This is a different holiday from what you would normally experience at an all inclusive hotel vacation.
